wtfCommit.providerOverrides.markdownDescription:
Custom Base URL and Model specifically for each AI provider. Overrides the global settings.

**Example in `settings.json`:**
```json
{
  "DeepSeek": {
    "baseUrl": "https://api.deepseek.com/beta",
    "model": "deepseek-coder"
  },
  "Custom": {
    "baseUrl": "https://my-custom-endpoint.com/v1",
    "model": "my-custom-model"
  }
}
```
